name: Echoes of Prophecy I: Repentance
description:
Echoes of Prophecy is a collaborative series between @aebrer and @celad00r. Each piece is reimagined through the lens of AI to reveal the visions buried within. 

The pieces in this four-part release are all based on https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/210090 . Minted first is the video of the prophecy itself, followed by the distilled frame of each stanza of the prophecy.
